Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Agora não consigo me mexer... Isso é meu destino, mas...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Não desistirei mais porque acordei.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Meu coração queimando e pulsante reflete esta era...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}uma paixão queima intensamente
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.72,0:00:35.68,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Chorando, embora eu não possa ver agora...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.68,0:00:40.23,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Um marco de busca flutua à frente.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.03,0:00:53.32,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Vou levar o que resta da minha juventude para lá.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.05,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Se estes lábios secos ficarem úmidos,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.55,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Além do tempo, rumo a uma era apaixonada,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.26,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Porque eu acredito que vai se mover...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Embora não possa mudar agora seja o destino,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Pois já despertei e não vou desistir.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}A empolgação ardente reflete a época,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Um fogo que arde brilhantemente.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.72,0:00:35.68,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Chorando, agora também fica invisível.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.68,0:00:40.23,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Um caminho procurado flutua.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.23,0:00:43.27,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Quero ter um tempo puro!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.27,0:00:48.03,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Todo mundo tem uma mente nobre!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.03,0:00:53.32,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}O despertar da juventude que permaneceu lá.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.99,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Acreditando em um sinal de Zeta,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.99,0:01:00.62,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Além dos tempos dif
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.05,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}se minha boca estiver molhada
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.55,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}o tempo fluirá para uma era quente
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.26,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Eu acredito que ele está em perigo.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.14,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}Acreditando em um sinal de Zeta,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.14,0:01:23.77,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0\fad(200,200)}para além dos tempos difíceis que ainda estão por vir
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Agora não consigo me mexer... É meu destino, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não desistirei mais porque percebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Meu coração queimando e pulsante reflete a era...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Ele tem a cor de chamas que ardem vividamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:35.68,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Chorando, embora não possa ver agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:40.23,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Procurando, um marco flutua à frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:53.32,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Vou usar o que resta da minha energia lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.05,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Se esses lábios secos ficarem úmidos,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.55,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Além do tempo, em direção a uma era apaixonada,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.26,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Porque eu acredito que ele se moverá...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:15.50,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Agora é tarde demais para fazer algo sobre isso
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:20.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não desistirei mais a partir de agora
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:25.67,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}<o batimento do meu coração marca o fim de uma era>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Uma chama que arde mesmo no gelo mais frio
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:35.68,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Ah, como eu sinto falta de tomo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:40.23,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Perdi meu caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:43.27,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu quero ter um momento puro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:48.03,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Todo mundo tem uma mente nobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:53.32,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.99,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Acreditando em um sinal de Zeta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:00.62,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}além dos tempos difíceis que virão!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.05,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Se minha boca estiver molhada de saliva
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.55,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}O tempo segue em direção à era intensa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:16.26,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Por acreditar que ele vai acordar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.14,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Acreditando em um sinal de Zeta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:23.77,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0.5\fad(200,200)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}além dos tempos difíceis a partir de agora...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.90,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Eu sempre acreditei que nos reencontraríamos desde aquele dia
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.90,0:23:01.07,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Se tivermos coração, seremos chamados juntos novamente
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.07,0:23:11.45,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Desperte a energia infinita
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.45,0:23:17.08,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Antes de você se machucar
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.08,0:23:23.17,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Encontre o que você pode fazer... Por favor
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.17,0:23:28.51,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Não jogue fora por causa desta idade dolorosa
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.85,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Até o dia em que voltarmos a olhar
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.85,0:23:38.52,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}para o céu azul que vimos uma vez
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.89,0:22:49.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Ah, não consigo deixar de acreditar em você.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.90,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}<eu acreditei em você até agora>
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.90,0:23:01.07,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Se ainda houver um coração que chama
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.07,0:23:11.45,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Invoco a Energia do Infinito
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.45,0:23:17.08,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Ah, ferido assim!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.08,0:23:23.17,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0} Procuro coisa possível, Por favor
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.17,0:23:28.51,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Quando estiver sofrendo, por favor, aguente
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.85,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}eu vi o céu azul algum dia
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.85,0:23:38.52,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1\bord0}Putting it all together, the best translation would be: "Até o dia em que eu te encontrar de novo." This translates to "Until the day I meet you again," preserving the idea of a definitive future encounter while maintaining the informal tone and using the correct verb tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.90,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu tenho acreditado que nos encontraremos novamente desde aquele dia
